{"id_resto": "g1439404-d12910992", "id_comment": "g1439404-d12910992-r747367595", "resto": "Masala_Inn_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1439404-d12910992-Reviews-Masala_Inn_Restaurant-Bexleyheath_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Musical chairs", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "24 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Janeandnick2014", "Many thanks for taking the time to review the Masala Inn Restaurant. I am very pleased to read that you enjoyed the foods and polite staff. however I am sorry to hear your unsatisfaction with the table selection during the dinner with us, I have addressed the issue with our front Manager for improvement customer expectation and allocating table efficiently .once again apologies for misleading experience.", "we hope to welcome you back for a better experience at the Masala Inn Bexleyheath.", "Warmest Regards ", "Management - The Masala Inn "], "reviewer_pseudo": "janeandnick2014", "reviewer_origin": ["Bexleyheath, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1439404-d12910992-r747367595-Masala_Inn_Restaurant-Bexleyheath_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I will start by saying the staff polite as ever... busy .. clean restaurant... couldn\u2019t fault the food.", "We booked our table for two in advance... arrived and was offered the little table by the door... too busy with the bar... people arriving... leaving and takeaways. We asked for another table which we were happy to wait for... We were finally seated... relaxed and ordered our food... it was busy so the food arrival was going to take a little while. Just before our food was due to be served.. A waiter politely asked us if we could move... a family of six were waiting for larger seated area.. so we had to move to another table.. not much better than the one we declined earlier... We finished our meal and just wanted to leave... it felt like musical chairs... We are in no hurry to rush back.. it is not always about the food...."]}
