{"id_resto": "g1646063-d1946997", "id_comment": "g1646063-d1946997-r724815251", "resto": "B_K_Salt_Beef_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1646063-d1946997-Reviews-B_K_Salt_Beef_Bar-Edgware_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The Best Salt Beef and Latkas around!", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "7 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Cadillacsts4600", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1646063-d1946997-r724815251-B_K_Salt_Beef_Bar-Edgware_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["A small friendly, long established, family run Salt Beef restaurant with the best salt beef around. They cure their own salt beef and it is always excellent - moist and flavourful. Amazingly good as a sandwich with mustard on rye bread, with a latka and a couple of fried fish balls if you are really hungry and very greedy! The chopped liver, egg and onion, tongue and pickles are great too, though I've never been a fan of turkey. I just can't ever manage to fit everything in, in a single visit as the portions are very generous. I've been coming here for my regular Salt Beef fix for decades and it has never failed to please. What more can you say about BK .... unassuming but definitely one of the best."]}
