{"id_resto": "g616258-d9459575", "id_comment": "g616258-d9459575-r726404489", "resto": "Niyom_Thai_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g616258-d9459575-Reviews-Niyom_Thai_Restaurant-Denham_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "If Thai be the food of choice, eat on", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "14 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ranjitryatt7", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "77"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "208"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g616258-d9459575-r726404489-Niyom_Thai_Restaurant-Denham_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Niyom Thai Restaurant is people friendly. Cross the threshold into the restaurant and the first thing that becomes apparent is this place is unmistakably Thai. The restaurant has clean lines, is tastefully decorated and white linen-covered tables are well spaced for comfort and privacy. For convenience, there is ample free parking around.", "Customarily, Thai restaurants serve Singha and Tiger beers but this is one of a handful of Thai restaurants that also serves Chang Thai Beer. I often use an adapted cliche here which says 'Chang beer refreshes parts other beers can't reach'.", "The hallmark of a good restaurant is the menu and variety of dishes the eating house fronts. Niyom boasts a very extensive and varied menu that is designed to cater for the gastronomic requirements and palates of most diners. ", "Niyom's aspiration is 'if it's not on the menu, please ask and we will do our utmost (within reason) to cook the dish for you or tweak an existing one to your taste'. As an example, my friend and I had Prawn Tamarind (giant grilled prawns served on a bed of crispy noodle topped with an exotic sweet and sour tamarind sauce), which were delicious. I inquired of Arm, our friendly and helpful waiter, whether they could replace the tamarind sauce with lemongrass, chilli and garlic sauce. He confirmed that would not be a problem. I also asked if they could cook steamed sea bass, which is currently not on the menu. Again he answered in the affirmative.", "Niyom's flexible approach in customising a dish to the diner's preference is refreshing and, indeed, worth pondering.", "All in all, we had an enthralling eating experience on our return visit this lunch time and look forward to the next one with anticipation."]}
{"id_resto": "g616258-d9459575", "id_comment": "g616258-d9459575-r728231685", "resto": "Niyom_Thai_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g616258-d9459575-Reviews-Niyom_Thai_Restaurant-Denham_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous Thai food", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "22 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "655jennym", "reviewer_origin": ["Fleet, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g616258-d9459575-r728231685-Niyom_Thai_Restaurant-Denham_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["We visited here for the second time last night. The food was gorgeous. Authentic Thai dishes presented beautifully and probably the best I ve tasted. Lovely intimate restaurant and welcoming, friendly owners. Highly recommend."]}
