{"id_resto": "g1566233-d2510361", "id_comment": "g1566233-d2510361-r733436560", "resto": "The_Codfather", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1566233-d2510361-Reviews-The_Codfather-Northolt_Ealing_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Check your order !", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "18 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear Walterwy", "I apologize for the mistake and inconvenience we have caused.Our regular service guy Ergun has had a heart conditions and was off sick and a new staff started and he has mixed up the orders.", "If you had given us a call we could prepare and deliver the large cod and chips right away.", "However if you give us a call ask for Hakan we would like to put it right for you.", "Thanks "], "reviewer_pseudo": "walterwy", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1566233-d2510361-r733436560-The_Codfather-Northolt_Ealing_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I ordered, and paid for \"Large cod and chips\" , and was charged 9.80, that was fine.", "Unfortunately when i got home i realised that i had been supplied with an extra large portion of chips and a small portion of \"cod bites\" (a much cheaper meal ) - not happy!"]}
{"id_resto": "g616258-d9459575", "id_comment": "g616258-d9459575-r734448128", "resto": "Niyom_Thai_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g616258-d9459575-Reviews-Niyom_Thai_Restaurant-Denham_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointing Night Out!", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "24 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "markrZ1821QB", "reviewer_origin": ["Ickenham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g616258-d9459575-r734448128-Niyom_Thai_Restaurant-Denham_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Having read some great reviews of this restaurant, my friends and I visited here a few weeks back and being lovers of Thai cuisine we were really looking forward to it. However, we all left feeling a little disappointed as the food did not live up to expectations. Service was mixed and food was rushed out even though we had said to take time between courses, some staff very friendly, others not so, drinks were a bit expensive but most importantly, the food was a bit bland, some dishes were cold & overall they lacked flavour & dare I say freshness & authenticity, Maybe the restaurant has new owners, maybe it was an off night, maybe it was a different or new chef that night but I\u2019m sorry to say that compared to Sukanya which is our normal \u201cgo to\u201d place we were not impressed."]}
