{"id_resto": "g1566233-d2510361", "id_comment": "g1566233-d2510361-r728269505", "resto": "The_Codfather", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1566233-d2510361-Reviews-The_Codfather-Northolt_Ealing_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Monkfish sold as cod", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "22 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear Moncod", "Thank for the leaving review.", "However you are so wrong with your accusations.The monk fish is known as lophious is very tasty and rare fish and almost 4 times more expensive then the cod fish.They retail around \u00a345 per kilo,and it would be impossible to sell as cod.", "Here as Codfather we aim to give best quality fish and customer service and if you are not happy with your food please get in touch with us tell the problem and we gladly rectify the problem.", "we would like to see you again.", "thanks"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Monkcod", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1566233-d2510361-r728269505-The_Codfather-Northolt_Ealing_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I have lived in this area for 18 years,I\u2019ve been too most fish and chips shops in the Northolt area. Yes I thought I\u2019d found the one decent fish and chips shop. Too my surprise yesterday I was given monkfish as cod, from CODFATHER. Great staff, poor food. Too think you can getaway with conning the local\u2019s. I\u2019LL NEVER EAT THERE AGAIN"]}
