{"id_resto": "g1637597-d3611128", "id_comment": "g1637597-d3611128-r744484293", "resto": "Madisons", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1637597-d3611128-Reviews-Madisons-Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great as always", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "11 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JasonBradley", "reviewer_origin": ["Bromley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1637597-d3611128-r744484293-Madisons-Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Havent been out for a meal in a long time but booked Madisons as local and fancied bbq ribs. Staff very attentive on arrival and during our stay, owner remembered me from 2 years ago and was exactly like I remembered him. As I've said I'm no regular customer but the food was delicious as before. I know it's maybe not hard to do ribs, but consistency is as we all know and the menu and food still is. How many burger joints open and close in bromley, I think Madisons is over 20 years strong if I remember rightly. It still has the same character, quality, and cleanliness I remember. Might sound strange ( I am) but If you try it just look at the $1 dollar bill's (notes) signed by hundreds of previous customers then placed on the walls. They still look brand new!"]}
