{"id_resto": "g186338-d12992337", "id_comment": "g186338-d12992337-r740329240", "resto": "Sahara_Grill_Hounslow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12992337-Reviews-Sahara_Grill_Hounslow-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Checking out Sahara Grill ", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "20 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "K9066KUandreaw", "reviewer_origin": ["Isleworth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12992337-r740329240-Sahara_Grill_Hounslow-London_England.html", "content": ["I'd been watching this restaurant for sometime while it was being set up and then when it opened. I just watched for a while to see how it got on and notice that they started to get quite a lot of people so walking around the high street in November I decided to go in for my dinner. Staff were so polite obviously been trained in customer service. The young man that saw me to my seat answered all my questions as if it wasn't any bother and was enjoying what he was doing with making suggestions too. The place is well kept, very clean and the different aromas that was coming from the different dishes was so nice but obviously I couldn't order everything. So, I ordered flame grilled chicken with chips and salad and must say I thoroughly enjoyed it. I'd recommend this restaurant for the food, decor and good customer service. ", "I wi be trying something else very soon.", "Oh, and they do take away. "]}
