{"id_resto": "g1637597-d18190867", "id_comment": "g1637597-d18190867-r747293786", "resto": "Istanbul_Grill", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1637597-d18190867-Reviews-Istanbul_Grill-Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely food and Great Cocktails", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "24 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PinkEgg78", "reviewer_origin": ["West Malling, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "86"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1637597-d18190867-r747293786-Istanbul_Grill-Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here for the first time yesterday with some friends for lunch. The restaurant itself is lovely and big and well presented, we started with some lovely cocktails and ordered a starter each which were very tasty, i had the baked Goats Cheese which i would highly recommend, it was really good. My main of chicken wings chips and salad were also very nice and portions are big, so make sure you go with an appetite. Service was exceptional, Beccy was attentive, helpful and very friendly so the afternoon flowed really nicely. ", "As it was a Sunday it was quite quiet but this wasn't a problem for us as we just ordered some more cocktails and had a good catch up, leaving after around 2.5 hours, but i would imagine it has a great buzzy atmosphere on a Friday/Saturday night. ", "It was a really nice meal and i'd recommend this restaurant if you're in the area."]}
