{"id_resto": "g1466790-d2013813", "id_comment": "g1466790-d2013813-r746474896", "resto": "Q_Verde", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1466790-d2013813-Reviews-Q_Verde-Kew_Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Authentic taste of the Amalfi coast in Kew", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "21 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nero T", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "54"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1466790-d2013813-r746474896-Q_Verde-Kew_Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We had a wonderful birthday dinner at our new favourite local Italian restaurant in Kew. ", "The owners and staff were so welcoming we felt like family and everything we had tasted superb - fresh and authentic. Standout starters were the homemade black Truffle Ravioli and the Calamari, and for mains, Vitello Saltimbocca and Rigatoni Arrabiata. Along with our Cioccolata & Arancia the owner Geraldo brought us a lovely dessert from his home town along with limoncellos and we celebrated with him and his family. ", "Altogether a warm, delightful evening which we would be happy to repeat. Grazie Mille Geraldo!"]}
