{"id_resto": "g2183309-d9740767", "id_comment": "g2183309-d9740767-r731203200", "resto": "La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2183309-d9740767-Reviews-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Splendido!!!", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "7 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jesse_Esquire", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2183309-d9740767-r731203200-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Compelled to share my recent experience of this true gem of an Italian restaurant. My wife who was working on a recent production at Pinewood studios told me how wonderful and authentic this family run restaurant was. Having read some recent reviews i was slightly sceptical, however, we ate there last week and must say that any concerns were dispelled and that it was a delight. The service was warm, efficient and the food was outstanding with a clear initiative to use on the finest fresh ingredients. Will be sure to visit again soon! Thanks for a wonderful experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g2183309-d9740767", "id_comment": "g2183309-d9740767-r726851430", "resto": "La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2183309-d9740767-Reviews-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nothing to write home about,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "16 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear Sir/ Madam ", "La Palma take good reviews and bad very serious, that helps us to improve on our daily service.", "Unfortunately I can not change your view on our decor or other remarks that you made.", "But going to the coffe machine unfortunately that evening when we reopened the restaurant we found out that one of the main pressure valves had a issue, we did try and call out the technician and he did come after 22.30 after closing time to fix the issue.", "My waiters had been briefed of the issue and they did serve Teas and Americano coffees and flat white that where prepared in the kitchen.", "Most likely you did not ask for alternative ,or your self was to busy writing the review seeing that you do so in every restaurant you have eating in and I am very amazed that you have a point in every place you have been.", "Please forgive me Sir when you do find the wright restaurant le me know I might try it my self.", "The Director"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GordonBeasley", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "202"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "83"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2183309-d9740767-r726851430-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["We dined here on recommendation but frankly were disappointed as we failed to find the 'wow' factor. Nothing particularly stood out and whilst nothing wrong with the food, service or deco it was just average. Quite a small restaurant that was quite noisy and normal conversation not always possible. Drinks expensive.", "The coffee machine here had been broken all day so no drinks availabke to round off the meal. We thought this particularly poor as they coukld have got a jar of normal and decaf in to offer something. To end on a positive we didnt have pizzas but they looked very good."]}
{"id_resto": "g2183309-d9740767", "id_comment": "g2183309-d9740767-r736971807", "resto": "La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2183309-d9740767-Reviews-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Saturday Delight", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "5 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GFwarrior", "reviewer_origin": ["Northampton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "321"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "136"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2183309-d9740767-r736971807-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Back in Slough, as our Daughter started her course at Iver, we found this little gem of a restaurant on an earlier Sojourn. ", "The food and service is simply superb, delightful pasta (superb #glutenfree), fantastic Casato Prosecco, finished off with a delightful dessert and coffee, what more can you ask for.", "Sensibly priced, family run restaurant, authentic, genuine we love it. ", "Our daughters course last 8 months, this will be our No1 destination when we visit."]}
