{"id_resto": "g2183309-d9740767", "id_comment": "g2183309-d9740767-r737672456", "resto": "La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2183309-d9740767-Reviews-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just excellent ", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "7 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "CheshireDancingqueen", "reviewer_origin": ["Nantwich, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "594"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "280"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2183309-d9740767-r737672456-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["We used to really like this restaurant when it was Palm Suite and it has been some time since we visited. ", "We were looking for somewhere to meet a friend close to the M40, the reviews looked good so we decided to give it a go on a Sunday lunchtime - what a find. ", "We had the most delightful arrabbiata as well as seafood pasta, not the slightest complaint from any of the 3 of us. The food was spectacular as was the house wine. ", "The service was attentive without being gushing (which I hate!). The bill a very welcome surprise, fantastic value. We can\u2019t recommend this place highly enough, a tremendous find. "]}
{"id_resto": "g2183309-d9740767", "id_comment": "g2183309-d9740767-r739654735", "resto": "La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2183309-d9740767-Reviews-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Meal for 2 ladies doing lunch", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "17 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "cindyd79", "reviewer_origin": ["Slough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "142"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2183309-d9740767-r739654735-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Meal for 2 ladies doing lunch", "Have eaten here a few times in the past.", "We did book but there were plenty of tables free. People did seem to be coming in for take away meals which I didn\u2019t know they did.", "We shared a tomato garlic bread to start. My friend had a chicken pasta dish and I had mushroom pasta ... food was delightful. Staff really nice not in your face but there if needed.. didn\u2019t have room for a pudding.. good value for money I will be visiting again ..."]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d4297495", "id_comment": "g504167-d4297495-r720078809", "resto": "Thanh_s_Bistro", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d4297495-Reviews-Thanh_s_Bistro-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Tasty food, friendly service", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "21 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Amelia C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d4297495-r720078809-Thanh_s_Bistro-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We had a lovely meal here on a busy Friday evening (we booked in advance which is recommended - they had to turn a few people away around 8:45pm).", "The waitress was friendly and welcoming upon arrival and attentive throughout. We had a starter and a main each and were very satisfied. Well sized portions and great flavours (we both had peanut curries but can't wait to try others!)", "It's a small restaurant and it seemed quite loud inside (it didn't really bother us) but this would probably be noticed less in a larger group of people. ", "We brought our own red wine with us which we kept at the table, but we saw that people with cold drinks could keep them in the fridge which is good to know for future!", "The food isn't as cheap as you might expect for a local restaurant but for the quality of the food we didn't mind at all. We'll be coming back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d4154575", "id_comment": "g186338-d4154575-r745868407", "resto": "Beirut_Nights", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d4154575-Reviews-Beirut_Nights-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sabahat was excellent\nI was", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "18 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ashh727", "reviewer_origin": ["Nairobi, Kenya"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d4154575-r745868407-Beirut_Nights-London_England.html", "content": ["Sabahat was excellent ", "I was there on valentines ", "She made it extra special, great great customer service, polite, considerate overall she made our experience amazing ", "I would love to come back when Sabahat is on shift "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d4154575", "id_comment": "g186338-d4154575-r746763080", "resto": "Beirut_Nights", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d4154575-Reviews-Beirut_Nights-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Food mediocre", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "22 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "OreoC81", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d4154575-r746763080-Beirut_Nights-London_England.html", "content": ["I think to be fair that this is a shisha place only, and that the food is a add on rather than the other way round, which basically means don\u2019t go there is you will not be smoking and expecting good food!", "We went on a Sat afternoon, the young waiter showed us inside, which was totally empty and it was pitch black. Eventually he turned the light up a fraction but we were still sat in what can only be described as darkness. After giving us some tired, greasy menus he left to go outside to smoke shisha. I ordered the baby chicken, which smelt really bad when it arrived, and my friend had the hamburger which was equally disgusting. The meat/chicken at this place just tastes off. Drinks arrive more than 50% being ice, and priced at \u00a35+ you expect a bit more drink for your money! The bill arrived at over \u00a350, which if the food is good would be worth it, but we felt cheated. Don\u2019t go there is you want an authentic Lebanese foodie experience, def make the trip to Edgware Road."]}
{"id_resto": "g2183309-d9740767", "id_comment": "g2183309-d9740767-r742582847", "resto": "La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2183309-d9740767-Reviews-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Authentic Italian restaurant that is a hidden treasure!", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "2 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Philip B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2183309-d9740767-r742582847-La_Palma_Italian_Restaurant-Iver_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["We were out on a long hike and, finding ourselves in Iver Heath at lunchtime, used Trip Advisor to find the best place to eat. By coincidence we were only 100 m away at the time, although we could have easily missed it as it is a little off the beaten track.", "The restaurant itself is superb. It offers authentic food that is up to the standards we are used to when visiting Italy. As the picture shows, the white tablecloths and smart appearance make for relaxed dining but it would also be suitable for a business meeting. ", "There is a huge choice of food on the menu. My wife had Fusilia Romana whilst I had Pollo Milanese. Both were delicious, freshly made and with generous portion sizes. We felt that our meal was good value for money. Now that we have found it, will be definitely be coming back with family and friend."]}
