{"id_resto": "g528819-d4939995", "id_comment": "g528819-d4939995-r744104068", "resto": "The_Bloomsbury_Pub", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g528819-d4939995-Reviews-The_Bloomsbury_Pub-Twickenham_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent food & friendly atmosphere", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "10 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "HeatherWelshgirl", "reviewer_origin": ["Twickenham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g528819-d4939995-r744104068-The_Bloomsbury_Pub-Twickenham_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["In truth we haven't been in the Bloomsbury for years even though we live 5 minutes away....but we were hearing so many good things about the pub we had to go and see for ourselves. We were not disappointed! We had family down on a Saturday and wanted to watch the Rugby. I had called ahead to check the Welsh game was on, unfortunately we were told it wasn't which was fine we would have tried the Bloomsbury another day...BUT I then had a call from the landlady (owner)r saying she had made a mistake and \"Yes\" the Rugby would be on, talk about going the extra mile for your customers-I was blown away by this. We of course went there & had a great few hours and loved chatting to the owners about the decor, food etc. The food look FAB but we already had plans for the Saturday evening,however we went back this Friday to try the Fish & Chips we were not disappointed it was Excellent!!!! This is a real GEM in the local area & you would be missing a true experience if you dont go.....Enjoy...We will see you there, as we are making it our new local :-) "]}
