{"id_resto": "g2536732-d5062724", "id_comment": "g2536732-d5062724-r723597845", "resto": "Dan_Thai", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2536732-d5062724-Reviews-Dan_Thai-Purley_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Takeaway ", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "3 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear Lauren Thom", "Thank you for choosing Dan Thai for your takeaway meal on Sunday, November 3rd. I am pleased that you found the meal to be authentic and very tasty.", "We strive to provide the best possible experience to all of our customers, takeaway or eat in.", "We are disheartened to hear that you are disappointed with the size of the takeaway's portions. ", "Given that we source the finest and freshest ingredients, most of our main dishes price is at \u00a36.95. The tiger prawns we used on Pad Thai noodles were more prominent than average. We used a long container for Noodles and special fried rice as theses are meals on its own. We used a shorter box for any other dishes. ", "We appreciate your feedback. It is what keeps us improving.", "We hope we can welcome you again, eat-in or takeaway.", "With Best Regards", "Pamela Sinlapa"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LaurenThom", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "102"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "36"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2536732-d5062724-r723597845-Dan_Thai-Purley_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I can\u2019t comment on the service as I had a takeaway, but the staff seemed very friendly.", "The pad thai was authentic and very tasty, but disappointingly only contained 4 prawns. The portion of chicken pad mee mao was also very stingy. The takeaway container was half the size of the pad thai container and wasn\u2019t even full. Usually the averaged sized take away dish would feed two people, but these are just about big enough for one.", "Again, the food was very tasty, just a shame that the portions are so small. "]}
