{"id_resto": "g2536732-d5062724", "id_comment": "g2536732-d5062724-r731504765", "resto": "Dan_Thai", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g2536732-d5062724-Reviews-Dan_Thai-Purley_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A taste of Thailand in Purley", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "9 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SangaSang", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "257"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g2536732-d5062724-r731504765-Dan_Thai-Purley_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["This review is for a Saturday night for a party of 3, we pre-booked our table. ", "This restaurant was full, however this is a small and cosy restaurant.", "I have travelled all over Thailand so many times, I thought I was back there after eating such lovely authentic Thai food. If you have never been to Thailand come here, you will understand what a treat it is to visit Thailand.", "We noticed that alot of people visit and get takeaways.", "Staff were so friendly, typical sweet, kind lovely Thai people.", "We will be back, so glad this is local to us."]}
