{"id_resto": "g504175-d4975690", "id_comment": "g504175-d4975690-r739345273", "resto": "Trattoria_Calabrese", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d4975690-Reviews-Trattoria_Calabrese-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect pizza and pasta", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "15 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "kjc242", "reviewer_origin": ["Kew, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d4975690-r739345273-Trattoria_Calabrese-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We found this little Italian gem close to Norbiton train station whilst we were visiting Kingston Hospital. ", "It was a 3 minute stroll and definitely worth the trip. ", "A small, cute, well decorated restaurant that was inviting as soon as we stepped in at 6pm. ", "The waiter was super gregarious and welcoming, spending a little time chatting to us which was really nice. ", "We ordered a pizza and a pasta dish and they arrived freshly made within 15-20 mins and we\u2019re both outstanding. ", "They were delicious and we polished them off with no hesitation. ", "I would highly recommend anyone to visit. "]}
{"id_resto": "g504175-d4975690", "id_comment": "g504175-d4975690-r741188710", "resto": "Trattoria_Calabrese", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d4975690-Reviews-Trattoria_Calabrese-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Authentic & Professional", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "25 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Curiosity759908", "reviewer_origin": ["Birmingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d4975690-r741188710-Trattoria_Calabrese-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["What a find! Thank you world-wide-web. 18.25 Saturday (Today Jan 25th):", "- me \"Do you have a table for 2\"", "- front of house \"Yes if can free the table by 20.00!\"", "- me \"Done.\"", "Swift, professional service by a Calabrian (OK Calabrese if you prefer). Being a soup man I was about to have the soup of the day (mushroom with a little broccoli which seemed plenty good enough) when I was informed of the fish soup. Good advice & good choice by me.", "The portions are on the large side - fish soup - probably, the ham and cheese - very!", "My wife could not finish her lasagne so they offered us to take it away. :) ", "House wine (southern Italian merlot) very satisfactory. Bill very prompt :). As I say, most professional. \u00a360 for two in SW London, Saturday night.", "Nobody's perfect but this was pretty close."]}
{"id_resto": "g504175-d4975690", "id_comment": "g504175-d4975690-r742558629", "resto": "Trattoria_Calabrese", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d4975690-Reviews-Trattoria_Calabrese-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "We had a charming evening", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "2 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ThePlumber19", "reviewer_origin": ["Kingston Upon Thames"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d4975690-r742558629-Trattoria_Calabrese-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We had a charming evening at the Trattoria Calabrese Restaurant last night. Gianni\u2019s welcome and attentiveness were faultless and the food yummy. We ate delicious portions of calamari, rare steak cooked to perfection, a scrumptious seafood risotto and pizza cooked on their pizza oven. Our shared panna cotta (replete with birthday candle and rendition) was the perfect sweet ending to our meal. We accompanied our meal with a delicious red from the excellent wine selection - the perfect way to end our dry January. "]}
