{"id_resto": "g1934185-d7797109", "id_comment": "g1934185-d7797109-r726400360", "resto": "BR6", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1934185-d7797109-Reviews-BR6-Orpington_Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely Lunch", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "14 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "2christinee", "reviewer_origin": ["Welling, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "64"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "95"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1934185-d7797109-r726400360-BR6-Orpington_Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["My partner and I had lunch here yesterday and was very impressed", "The restaurant is very light and welcoming.", "The Trainer /Front of house was very efficient and very supportive to his students.", "The food was very good.", "I had the fish Cake starter followed by the stuffed Chicken supreme and my partner had the Smoked Duck with Steak as his Main course.", "We had a bottle of the Cote du Rhone.", "The Student was shown how to present it to us and how to open the bottle and what to do with regards the tasting of the Wine.", "This I thought was most impressive and will stand him in great stead as he goes on in his career.", "The only small criticism I might have was the long wait between having our starter and receiving our Main course ", "but we took in account the Bakehouse which was very busy and the food was coming from the same kitchen.", "We will definitely return and lovely to support these up and coming students"]}
{"id_resto": "g1934185-d7797109", "id_comment": "g1934185-d7797109-r728601926", "resto": "BR6", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1934185-d7797109-Reviews-BR6-Orpington_Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Wonderful food", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "24 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Take_Me_Away_444", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "93"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1934185-d7797109-r728601926-BR6-Orpington_Bromley_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Attended a business event with a guest, where the Restaurant had been booked out specifically for the evening and we had all chosen our menu in advance from a varied set menu.", "The food was wonderful, the event itself excellent and the front of house very helpful. Not everything ran smoothly in the service, however, with it being a Student Led restaurant, this was not expected and things were corrected swiftly when required.", "Our 3 course dinner with wine was \u00a345 per head, but that included some money towards the Charity hosting the event, so is not indicitive of their typical prices, but even at that price it represents great value.", "Marking it fairly, I'm giving 4 out of 5 stars. If you allow for the fact that it's a Student led restaurant, it is of course 5 stars. Great work all involved, keep it up."]}
