{"id_resto": "g504167-d8471931", "id_comment": "g504167-d8471931-r724354533", "resto": "Yaalu_Yaalu_Selsdon", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d8471931-Reviews-Yaalu_Yaalu_Selsdon-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "3rd times a charm", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "6 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Rachel K", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d8471931-r724354533-Yaalu_Yaalu_Selsdon-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We dined here for the 3rd time last weekend and it gets better and better each time. If you love tasty food with a bit of spice then look no further, we have worked our way through a few things off the menu and everything we have tried is bursting with flavour! Food was served on a banana leaf which was a first for me but makes the expereince even more authentic. Service is spot on and food came out in a timely manor. I urge everyone to give this place a try, you will not be disappointed!"]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d8471931", "id_comment": "g504167-d8471931-r725211004", "resto": "Yaalu_Yaalu_Selsdon", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d8471931-Reviews-Yaalu_Yaalu_Selsdon-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and service", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "9 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Dennis S", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d8471931-r725211004-Yaalu_Yaalu_Selsdon-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Yaalu Yaalu this week (for the first time) with a friend from Munich. We all thought that the food was fantastic with great flavours and balanced spice and heat. We didn't realise how different a Sri Lankan menu would be from a Southern Indian one - and it's miles better! The staff member was friendly and informative, whilst also being professional and hard working. We will definitely be back soon!"]}
