{"id_resto": "g504167-d2627339", "id_comment": "g504167-d2627339-r734794649", "resto": "McDermott_s", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d2627339-Reviews-McDermott_s-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Gluten free. ", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "26 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jannabanna07", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d2627339-r734794649-McDermott_s-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Lovely fish and chips. We have eaten here several times. Sadly what lets it down is that on the last time we were there I was served an unsafe meal. I am coeliac and they either mixed up the two dishes or mine was seriously contaminated with gluten. I have never had such a bad coeliac reaction any other time so I suspect that I was given my husband\u2019s meal and he was given mine. I will never, ever go again as it takes me a really long time to recover from. If you don\u2019t have dietary requirements then definitely go as it\u2019s beautiful fish and chips. "]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d2627339", "id_comment": "g504167-d2627339-r740938898", "resto": "McDermott_s", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d2627339-Reviews-McDermott_s-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Gone down hill", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "24 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Hi Sam. Firstly may I apologise for your recent bad experience with us. We serve thousands of meals every week and occasionally do not hit the standards expected. What I hoped a regular customer would do is call, let us know and allow us to make it up to them. I'd be delighted to talk to you in person.", "kind regards, Sean McDermott, Owner."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sam S", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "147"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "45"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d2627339-r740938898-McDermott_s-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Last few times, have been disappointed by the quality.", "The fish looks fresh, but the last lot was almost raw in places, the batter has gone from crispy to greasy and the chips half cooked.", "After years of being a loyal customer, it\u2019s time to try elsewhere"]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d2627339", "id_comment": "g504167-d2627339-r741643327", "resto": "McDermott_s", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d2627339-Reviews-McDermott_s-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Saturday Night Supper", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "27 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "davidmM7045IU", "reviewer_origin": ["Bolton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "50"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d2627339-r741643327-McDermott_s-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Visiting friends in London they suggested fish and chips from a place the other side of Croydon to them. A little bit skeptical that they would survive the trip home we set off and arrived at a very busy establishment. Order placed for three cod and two chips (warned by my host that the chip portions were large). In quick time hot fish and chips were ready and bagged up. We set off at a dash (within the law of course) and arrived home, unpacked our hot delights and tucked in. They were as fresh as when packed and oh my..... Delicious!", "Crispy batter on perfect white flakes of cod, with crispy tasty chips.", "A sheer delight!"]}
