{"id_resto": "g504175-d1913037", "id_comment": "g504175-d1913037-r745756783", "resto": "Cappadocia", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d1913037-Reviews-Cappadocia-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "A ruined birthday celebration", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "17 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KristinaVKL", "reviewer_origin": ["Surbiton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d1913037-r745756783-Cappadocia-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I booked a table with a query of birthday candle in the dessert at the end for our 14 year old daughter. ", "When we arrived our table was still dirty. We waited 50 minutes for our drinks to arrive (finished starter by the time we got them) then another 25 mins for one missing drink. ", "No problem, as we love(d) this place so we were patient. ", "I went to the bar to remind the waiter to bring a candle with the birthday cake/dessert and to have birthday music playing. They said ok, even checked who the BD girl was.", "The waitresses were arguing next to us (with each other). Not too professional.", "We ordered dessert which arrived the ordinary way without a candle. ", "My daughter won\u2019t be 14 again. It was one of our favourite restaurant but we came home very upset and disappointed.", "When I mentioned this to the waiter he said a meaningless sorry. I doubt we\u2019ll go back again."]}
