{"id_resto": "g503784-d4553810", "id_comment": "g503784-d4553810-r735930467", "resto": "Riennas", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g503784-d4553810-Reviews-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Let down on News Eve.cocked up our booking.!!!!", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "31 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear 76ikh", "This was not a pleasant situation for us neither. ", "We surely didn\u2019t want to ruin your New Year\u2019s Eve and given you have been at our restaurant I am sure you have seen how much we care about every each customer and we want to make sure everyone at Rienna\u2019s enjoys their time. ", "Unfortunately this was something that we couldn\u2019t avoid because it was not our will to voluntarily cancelled your booking. ", "As I explained to you upon your arrival given We didn\u2019t have a deposit down a few weeks ago I tried to confirm your booking for New Years Eve, when I call the number I had saved ringed I didn\u2019t get an answer, straight someone called and cancelled the booking under your name. ", "Unfortunately I do not know what exactly happened If it was a strange coincidence or a misunderstanding,. ", "This was very upsetting as we do everything we can to avoid these kind of situations ( phone calls confirmation, emails, deposits etc) because unfortunately for unfortunate course of events I couldn\u2019t have predicted or in anyway avoided this from happening. ", "As I did mentioned to you last night if there is/was anything we could do for you, we happily would. ", "With all this said I just want to explain once again the facts and make you comprehend that this wasn\u2019t something we wished for, or did anything to make it happened, we do value and appreciate", "our customers and our work we make everything possible to make everyone have a good time at our restaurant. ", "I hope you understand our point of view. ", "We wish to see you again and wish you a very Happy New Year! "], "reviewer_pseudo": "76ikh", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g503784-d4553810-r735930467-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Booked in October for 3 people ,we are regular customers ,confirmed booking in December when we there with 5 friends.Only to arrive and be told we had no booking ,and was offered nothing .At 8.30 we now had to find somewhere that could accommodate us.Went to the Welcome Inn in Hornchurch,I can't thank them enough for finding us a table although they were fully booked .Will definitely not return to Rienna 's .They ruined our New Years Eve with out any type of compensation,just a sorry ."]}
{"id_resto": "g503784-d4553810", "id_comment": "g503784-d4553810-r738532814", "resto": "Riennas", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g503784-d4553810-Reviews-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "3rd visit to this restaurant ", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "11 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "719theresab", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "160"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "59"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g503784-d4553810-r738532814-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["3rd visit to this wonderful local restaurant. This cozy restaurant has a great menu. You need to book at the weekend. It was very busy when we went just before Christmas. The Chateaubriand is one of their standout dishes but honestly I have taken family and friends and none of us has been disappointed. I think it is currently the best restaurant in Hornchurch. "]}
{"id_resto": "g503784-d4553810", "id_comment": "g503784-d4553810-r740652536", "resto": "Riennas", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g503784-d4553810-Reviews-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Experience", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "22 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ColletteCo", "reviewer_origin": ["Milton Keynes, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g503784-d4553810-r740652536-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["With 9 people to satisfy, we usually struggle with everyone being satisfied but the whole family from 17 to 70 had a great experience. Food was plentiful and tasty and service good in a comfortable setting - a lovely celebration meal all round! "]}
{"id_resto": "g503784-d4553810", "id_comment": "g503784-d4553810-r740040812", "resto": "Riennas", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g503784-d4553810-Reviews-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "BAD RUDE BAD", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "19 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Hi Peter ", "We appreciate you taking your time writing this review however this reaction remains to us a big surprise .", "We only keep and serve fresh food to our customers and on a Sunday evening being that has been very busy all day it is possible that we might have run out of something. ", "Given the quality of ingredients is very important to us we hope that if that is the case our customers understand that. ", "Most of the time they do. ", "Now when you came in we kindly informed you straight away that we had run out of lobster. I would understand this kind of reaction if you had reserved lobster and on your arrival there wasn\u2019t any. ", " Your reaction was very powerful to not say rude towards us, given that we couldn\u2019t have known that you wanted lobster without you letting us know in advance. ", "We were and never will be rude to you or anyone as that does not suit our style. ", "It is fair that you paid for your drink you wouldn\u2019t dream of going into a supermarket and going out without paying, why should it be different in a restaurant. ", "All the best ", "Rienna\u2019s Staff "], "reviewer_pseudo": "O9766CBpeterl", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g503784-d4553810-r740040812-Riennas-Hornchurch_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Yesterday booked a table - then they called later on to say or booking had been canceled - second booking attempt today with our family - they took our drinks order without informing us first there was no lobster on the menu - So we left the restaurant hungry and the Rude waitress also insisted we pay for the drinks too - what a complete joke !"]}
