{"id_resto": "g191301-d7371292", "id_comment": "g191301-d7371292-r736886872", "resto": "Treviso_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191301-d7371292-Reviews-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor choice and service. Disappointing. ", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "4 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "davidcH1294DT", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191301-d7371292-r736886872-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We were disappointed to be given a very limited lunch menu today with no seafood pasta. I ordered Seafood Risotto which was poor with the seafood totalling only 4 prawns and 4 mussels. My wife\u2019s salmon pasta was ok. Later we saw other customers getting various dishes with clams and mussels and were told they were the many specials that someone should have told us about but hadn\u2019t! They also charged us for 250 ml glasses of wine when we did not ask for large. Poor communication and impersonal service. \u00a352 for above plus coffee. Left feeling very let down and that they didn\u2019t care. "]}
{"id_resto": "g191301-d7371292", "id_comment": "g191301-d7371292-r741607010", "resto": "Treviso_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191301-d7371292-Reviews-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very poor show", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "27 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "K8821YZlindap", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191301-d7371292-r741607010-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We had booked this restaurant for a special occasion and had travelled a long way only to find it closed!!!!! No phone call, no message left to inform us that they had a problem with the gas supply. After a Google search and a phone call to another Italian close by, we ended up in Sebastian's, which was outstanding. Great food and excellent customer service saved our day. Treviso, you could learn something from this restaurant!!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g191301-d7371292", "id_comment": "g191301-d7371292-r742534752", "resto": "Treviso_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191301-d7371292-Reviews-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "2 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Revduncan", "reviewer_origin": ["Birmingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "516"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "144"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191301-d7371292-r742534752-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I'm glad I booked because before too long they were turning people away.", "Not the largest restaurant but a warm Italian welcome. The menu is not large either but there is enough choice. Be sure to ask what the specials are. They didn't tell us until we came to order from the menu.", "Some of the descriptions of the dishes, in my view, promised more than they delivered such as the scallop starter - 2 scallops with four head and tail off regular prawns. Beautifully cooked though.", "The rib eye steak was very sinewy and after I'd fought my way through it I was offered a complimentary sirloin steak to make up for it. I should have spoken up sooner.", "Everyone enjoyed their food. Portions were good - no room for dessert.", "The wine list had a very good range of wines including many non Italian. Prices starting at \u00a322 bottle", "We would happily return."]}
{"id_resto": "g191301-d7371292", "id_comment": "g191301-d7371292-r741607335", "resto": "Treviso_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191301-d7371292-Reviews-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very disappointing - closed with no notice!", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "27 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nicola240189", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191301-d7371292-r741607335-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Drove to Treviso to celebrate my birthday with my family, including my baby son. My parents had travelled a long way to take us, and had confirmed booking the week before via phone. When we arrived, the restaurant was closed with a sign on the door saying \u201cclosed due to gas problems.\u201d We hadn\u2019t received a call, email or any kind of message as to the closure, which would have given us time to book somewhere else. The issue was not that they had had to close, it was that we had not been told. Luckily, with a hungry baby in tow, we managed to make a last minute booking at Sebastian\u2019s Italian down the road - which was absolutely fantastic from start to finish and I would thoroughly recommend. Luckily not a wasted trip for my family in the end!"]}
{"id_resto": "g191301-d7371292", "id_comment": "g191301-d7371292-r745161841", "resto": "Treviso_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191301-d7371292-Reviews-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Gorgeous little Italian restaurant", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "15 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "626sallyg", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191301-d7371292-r745161841-Treviso_Restaurant-Richmond_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Gorgeous little Italian restaurant in Kew - it\u2019s always packed and has a great atmosphere, charming and welcoming staff and the food is so delicious - yummy, yummy, yummy - what more can I say!"]}
