{"id_resto": "g7380842-d1415050", "id_comment": "g7380842-d1415050-r745680578", "resto": "Friends_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d1415050-Reviews-Friends_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely Restaurant", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "17 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SuesPinner_12", "reviewer_origin": ["Pinner, Middlesex"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d1415050-r745680578-Friends_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["This is an independant restaurant near to where we live. We decided to try their Sunday lunch set menu. We arrived slightly early but were shown straight to our table. The staff were very friendly. We ordered drinks whilst we chose our meals. After we had ordered our food we were given freshly cooked bread rolls which were delicious. I chose the vension sausages and my partner had the lamb. Both were delicious. We both opted for desserts - creme brule for me and chocolate delice for my partner. We had a lovely time. This will be added to our list."]}
{"id_resto": "g499486-d3185406", "id_comment": "g499486-d3185406-r703992887", "resto": "Humphry_s_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499486-d3185406-Reviews-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Simply Sublime...", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "28 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "binx892016", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499486-d3185406-r703992887-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["We are returning guests and have specific dietary requirements. Chris and his brigade go out of their way to exceed our expectations and make every visit utterly memorable. We eat out regularly in some fabulous restaurants but can honestly say Humphry's is the standout. ", "We would like to especially thank Chris and his brigade, Terry, Christian, Marta and Harry - you ace it!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g499486-d3185406", "id_comment": "g499486-d3185406-r702198887", "resto": "Humphry_s_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499486-d3185406-Reviews-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Birthday Treat", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "23 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "N2165FBjm", "reviewer_origin": ["Berkshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "68"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "63"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499486-d3185406-r702198887-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["My partner chose to take me to Humphreys, to celebrate my birthday. ", "On arrival, bearing in mind that Stoke Park is considered to be a prestigious place to stay, we felt we rather had a cold reception from the person at the front desk.", "We had arrived early, with a view to having pre dinner drinks in the grounds but were taken straight to the restaurant by a member of staff who had the appearance of a maintenance person.", "Quite disappointed so far. ", "However, when we arrived at Humphreys the quality and warmth of the staff was perfect. We were escorted out to the gardens and enjoyed pre dinner drinks.", "The food was delicious, with a good choice and variety of flavour, the service and attention of the staff was exemplary.", "However, the dining room itself was very shabby, in particular the carpets which smelt and were heavily stained throughout.", "All In all, we had a lovely evening but feel that Stoke Park is tired, tatty, smelly and is in need of refurbishment."]}
{"id_resto": "g7380842-d1415050", "id_comment": "g7380842-d1415050-r744913186", "resto": "Friends_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d1415050-Reviews-Friends_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely family celebration", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "13 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Benphil", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "127"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "39"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d1415050-r744913186-Friends_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We booked the upstairs room for a family lunch to celebrate a special anniversary. Maria was a delight to work with and a menu was chosen to accommodate everyone's dietary requirements, changing some recipes. Food was great and everyone had a lovely time."]}
{"id_resto": "g7380842-d1415050", "id_comment": "g7380842-d1415050-r745248962", "resto": "Friends_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d1415050-Reviews-Friends_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Superior Saturday lunch", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "15 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "BetF830", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d1415050-r745248962-Friends_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Five of us came for lunch on a Saturday, one of whom is 19 months old. The staff were very welcoming and accommodating. The lunch menu, although limited in scope, was varied and tempting. The food was all delicious and of a very high standard. It would be easy to think you were in a 2 star Michelin restaurant but without the fuss. Absolutely everything about the experience was better than 5 star. We're lucky to have such a fab restaurant in Pinner! Head and shoulders above most of the local competition!"]}
