{"id_resto": "g499486-d3185406", "id_comment": "g499486-d3185406-r734047451", "resto": "Humphry_s_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499486-d3185406-Reviews-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely setting, lovely fish courses, though limited choice for veggies", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "22 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Moleseyboy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "365"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "128"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499486-d3185406-r734047451-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["When reserving Humphry's I specifically asked whether vegetarians were catered for and was assured this was the case. In the event, the tasting menu was not accessible (mix of meat, fish and veggie) and the a la carte menu only had one veggie option as a starter and one as a main course. ", "What went well... My wife ordered trout as a starter and then halibut as a main course. Both were declared excellent! We had ordered a bottle of St Veran, which was excellent (Joseph Drouhin 2017). She then ordered the plum souffle, which was also lovely (she allowed me a taste), washed down with some dessert wine which was equally good (but whose name eludes me). The service from our Portuguese waiter was the perfect balance of friendliness, humour, authenticity, efficiency and knowledge - although I neglected to ask for his name, he is a credit to the restaurant.", "Now, some 'even better ifs'... it would have been even better if there was a wider selection of vegetarian options. That said, I was happy to order the Gnocchi as it sounded interesting, coming with parmesan waifers and pecan meringue. In the event it rather lacked flavour and I missed the pecan meringue in the dish: when I mentioned this to the maitre d' he pondered the question then claimed that it was included in the gnocchi themselves rather than separate. I found this surprising as there was no evidence to suggest this. In any event, it was somewhat underwhelming. I then ordered treacle tart - a particular favourite - but was informed a few minutes' later that it was no longer available. The waiter suggested the apple dish as an alternative. The apple itself was well-cooked and not too sweet, but the crumble seemed under-cooked. ", "I had ordered the mushroom buckwheat as a main and that was deeply flavoured, with some lovely complexity and a richness that was not overpowering. It was gobbled up with great relish.", "Overall, we very much enjoyed the experience, given all the plus points called out above, but it does disappoint me that vegetarians get a raw deal in terms of choice. I was also not overly wowed by my starter and dessert, which was a shame: to be clear, they were not 'bad' just not up to the same standard of excellence which my wife enjoyed. All the wines we ordered were top notch and the service from our waiter equally good. ", "Would we return? Yes, absolutely - the style of cooking and the ambience was very much to our liking."]}
{"id_resto": "g499486-d3185406", "id_comment": "g499486-d3185406-r740166437", "resto": "Humphry_s_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499486-d3185406-Reviews-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best meal for a long time", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "20 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Neil S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499486-d3185406-r740166437-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["The food quality here is extrememly high, the building wonderful and service really good. I've eaten in a lot of good restaurants around the world and this was the best overal experience for a very long time."]}
