{"id_resto": "g499486-d3185406", "id_comment": "g499486-d3185406-r747256317", "resto": "Humphry_s_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499486-d3185406-Reviews-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A Sparkly 40th indeed", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "24 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "snb-40", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499486-d3185406-r747256317-Humphry_s_Restaurant-Stoke_Poges_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Would like to say a very big thank you to all the staff at Stoke Park who made my 40th dinner on Thur 20th Feb very special indeed. My guest and I were given a beautiful table where we enjoyed stunning views of the beautiful grounds and grande rooms.The meal itself was absolutely\u00a0delicious. With so many extra tasty courses it certainly felt like the meal that kept giving. Each course was exceptional in taste and quality. I had the Gnocchi to start, Beef main and Apple crumble\u00a0souffle to finish.We finished off with complimentary\u00a0chocolates and an adorable sparkler birthday cupcake. The staff couldn't have made the dinner any more special and I highly recommend\u00a0for special\u00a0occasions or for a lovely treat. Thanks again Stoke Park for an exceptionally personalised experience."]}
