{"id_resto": "g1999999-d2515295", "id_comment": "g1999999-d2515295-r715322745", "resto": "Northwood_Piazza", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1999999-d2515295-Reviews-Northwood_Piazza-Northwood_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Disappointed", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "4 October 2019", "answer_text": ["We are very sorry that you were disappointed with your last visit to our restaurant. Our tables are always booked on a \u2018first come, first served\u2019 basis, unfortunately when you booked on Friday evening all the tables downstairs were full. However, had you mentioned when you called that there were elderly people in your group, we may have been able to re-arrange our tables for you, but if not, we would have explained that only the tables upstairs were now available for that evening. ", "You did mention during the evening that the food was not to your liking and as a goodwill gesture we did not charge you for any of your main courses. ", "We are deeply offended by your final comments which we consider to be unfair and completely untrue. Our tables are nearly always booked in advance by telephone according to specific requests, individual needs, availability and only to these criteria"], "reviewer_pseudo": "240harshap", "reviewer_origin": ["Northwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1999999-d2515295-r715322745-Northwood_Piazza-Northwood_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We walked in didn\u2019t feel welcomed were sent upstairs to eat. My elderly mum could hardly get up the stairs. Service by waiter was not bad but the food was not up to standard the pizza dough was burnt tasted bitter and the pasta was quite raw.. no salt I have eaten several times before used to be good not anymore. I noticed only white faces were set downstairs and brown people upstairs. Very sad in this day and age. Don\u2019t think I will be visiting there in a hurry."]}
