{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r737275106", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Messy wine-tasting", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "6 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RichS87", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "108"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "61"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r737275106-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["My friends and I booked the wine tasting here, where you get to taste 6 different types of wine (3 red, 3 white) and get a platter of cheese and meat with it.", "It didn't start off great, since we were plonked on a small table in a dingy corner. We'd requested the tasting room at the back upon booking, but this was ignored.", "It quickly became apparent that the barman was in charge of pouring our wines, whilst simultaneously tending to anyone at the bar ordering drinks. His knowledge was perfunctory (this wine is from *insert country*, it tastes of *insert flavour*, eat it with *insert cheese or meat*) when pouring it out.", "We repeatedly had to ask for the music to be turned down-after all, this is meant to be a wine-bar, not a nightclub, but despite this they turned it up- stating that that's the 'vibe' they were going for and that 'people want to dance'. Nonsense. ", "After much moaning we got moved to the tasting room at the back, probably just to shut us up. I don't remember leaving really, so I must have had at least a good night. I'd only recommend this place if you're looking for a casual wine-tasting experience and don't mind shouting across the table to your mates in order to be heard. Service was poor really, though the gentleman tried his best."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d9711469", "id_comment": "g186338-d9711469-r731187928", "resto": "Sowa_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d9711469-Reviews-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Shockingly poor manners!", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "7 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Hi anna321582019, ", "Thank you for taking the time to write a review. We appreciate your feedback.", "We're sorry to learn of your poor experience. If you can kindly write to us on contact@sowarestaurant.co.uk, we can look into this for you further. ", "We hope you'll give us another chance. ", "Kind regards, ", "The team at Sowa"], "reviewer_pseudo": "anna321582019", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d9711469-r731187928-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Came in for a coffee today with my friend turned out there was no place to sit, one of the ladies kindly asked if we could sit on the restaurant side even though we only wanted a coffee, we were told to take one of the tables once we were ready to sit another lady jumped into us saying we cannot sit here as it is reserved! I said that we have been told to take that table n can sit for one hour! I was told no u can\u2019t sit here u can see it\u2019s reserved and she started pointing to the reserved sign!! I said I can read that perfectly but we were told we can take this table ! After all we were placed at some other table and again another staff member said u can\u2019t sit here only for coffee it is restaurant!!! I said we were told to sit here cos of lack of the space on the other side!! I would understand everything but the worst thing is all of those people got zero manners! Absolutely undermining tone of voice!!! Never been to place like that before! Place is nice but people spoil the whole atmosphere!! I only write this review cos it is not first time I have experienced such a lack of manners!! Need new staff!!!"]}
