{"id_resto": "g186338-d2256999", "id_comment": "g186338-d2256999-r719894594", "resto": "Pentolina", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2256999-Reviews-Pentolina-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "First class authentic Italian ", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "20 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "526ritao", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2256999-r719894594-Pentolina-London_England.html", "content": ["What a gem this turned out to be! Excellent and authentic Italian food from a varied menu and all reasonably priced. Impressive wine list too. I had the rabbit with capers and black olives with spinach and mashed potatoes. All cooked to perfection and I am still drooling over the pear and ricotta torta! ", "Although the place was jam packed on a Friday night the service was impeccable. Only one regret: that I live in France and I'm not a local!! But I will be back for sure. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d2256999", "id_comment": "g186338-d2256999-r723464362", "resto": "Pentolina", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d2256999-Reviews-Pentolina-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Consistently good", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "3 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Marguerite C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "54"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d2256999-r723464362-Pentolina-London_England.html", "content": ["I dined here this week for the fourth time in the past three months. Always great service and food and notably a local but serious-food vibe. I started with the grilled octopus, followed by the grilled halibut, coupled with an unfiltered organic white wine from Italy, superb. The wine list is entirely Italian, not surprising. The wait staff is knowledgeable about the wine offering and quite helpful if you need to steer. Great place in the summer as well, the doors open and a few sidewalk tables are placed out in what is a sweet residential neighborhood. Highly recommend."]}
