{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r740813412", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful, classy and feels like London!", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "23 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "louiseromeah1", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r740813412-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I had an amazing experience at Basil and Grape. The staff were friendly and attentive, the food was divine! And the whole restaurant had a beautiful scenery, it made me feel like I was in central London. 10/10 no complaints!"]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r744532068", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely Late Lunch at the Basil and Grape with my Mum", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "12 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Karen A", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r744532068-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I usually have the pear and goats cheese salad which I love however this time had a goats cheese ciabatta. I was a little disappointed as the ciabatta seemed very thick but the filling was gorgeous. My Mum chose a pizza and thoroughly enjoyed it. We chose the light lunch menu and added \u00a33 to the deal to enjoy a large glass of wine. We had a coffee afterwards... the waiter forgot to ask what type which is very rare especially here. I gave us an espresso and we had to ask for warm milk. Coffee itself tasted very good. The whole lunch cost \u00a324. We were comfortable in one of the cosy booths. I would strongly recommend this restaurant/wine bar but if you want late lunch possible go a bit earlier than 3:30pm."]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r741272657", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Very nice setting, good food but poor service", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "26 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "clara l", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r741272657-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["The place is beautifully decorated and has a very nice atmosphere. The wine list is extensive and very good quality. We had pizza which were delicious. However we thought the service was really poor. Waiters did not know what was on the menu, forgot our desserts then were really rude when it came to the bill. It kind of put us off coming back again."]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r747039720", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Could do a lot better", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "23 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "seafoodaddict", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r747039720-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on the weekend - Sunday, we have been once before and really enjoyed it. This time was different. Opened the door to be greeted by a women sitting down on a stool doing paperwork. Told us to sit anywhere. We opted for a booth. No one came over for at least 10 mins because our waiter was talking to a group of people in the booth behind us for that time. No music and no atmosphere. Left without eating or a drink. Very disappointed, not good vibes at all. "]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r747286999", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Not as good as I expected", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "24 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SteveS1959", "reviewer_origin": ["Coventry, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r747286999-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Firstly, for a restaurant in Croydon I felt that we were paying central London prices. Secondly, the service was a bit hit and miss, although they did score a hit when a waiter ripped the cap off a bottle of wine for another table and I got splashed! Thirdly we were persuaded to have a Pinsa pizza which we all found to be a bit stodgy. On the plus side we started with a Suprema sharing platter which seemed expensive at \u00a348 but it was impressive, and combined with the bread baskets, meant that we only needed one pizza afterwards to share between the 4 of us. So if you do order the Suprema don't order anything else until we have completed it. In summary, the meal was OK but I wouldn't rush to go back."]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r747408086", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "A bit disappointing as had so many good reviews", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "24 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Brian S", "reviewer_origin": ["Carshalton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "61"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r747408086-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Opened the door and impressed with the interior, a friendly greeting, we found a booth which reduced the sound of the loud music.", "Disappointed as wine we ordered was not available but cleverly guided to a dearer bottle which turned out to be mediocre for the price. The menu is very limited and no pasta, settled for an over priced pizza each.", "Felt this was an okay glorified pizza restaurant, posing as a wine bar, charging West End prices in Croydon.", "Left leaving the bill and monies on the table, no goodbyes or thank you see you again soon.", "Will we return, he answer is NO."]}
{"id_resto": "g504167-d14150498", "id_comment": "g504167-d14150498-r747392180", "resto": "Basil_Grape", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504167-d14150498-Reviews-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a venue.\nEasily the best", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "24 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "126adamk", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504167-d14150498-r747392180-Basil_Grape-Croydon_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["What a venue.", "Easily the best venue in Croydon.", "Valentino is a top waiter, serve is excellent, the prices here are such good value compared to London!", "Well worth spending an evening with your mates or on a date.", "Good wine and delicious charcuterie boards. ", "This has become a regular restaurant due to the simple things being executed to perfection."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d9711469", "id_comment": "g186338-d9711469-r734039951", "resto": "Sowa_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d9711469-Reviews-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great food , shame about the slow service", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "22 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "monxxLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d9711469-r734039951-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited Sowa after reading great reviews - made a special trip from the outskirts of London. ", "The food was very good and the presentation great which many polish restaurants are lacking.", "Unfortunately, the service is somewhat disappointing. Despite the restaurant not being very busy - getting a menu involved the unnecessary wait and then it was going even more painful - waiting for starters which finally arrived - then a massive gap and wait for a main.", " After that, no one offered a dessert menu which I had to ask for. ", "From then on I gave up - tea and coffee arrived separately and the waiter forgot to deliver the desserts. ", "Good food, nice atmosphere - completely uninterested waiting staff."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d9711469", "id_comment": "g186338-d9711469-r731360538", "resto": "Sowa_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d9711469-Reviews-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great pastries", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "8 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Hello sheepygold,", "We are grateful for the kind words and compliment on our pastries. We promise to provide you with that same level of satisfaction or even more when you return!", "Kind regards,", "Sowa Restaurant"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sheepygold", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4571"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1817"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d9711469-r731360538-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We came in for a takeaway cake which is sold by weight. There is a large and varied choice to choose from. \u00a32.50 will get you a generous slice enough for 2. Quality and freshness is excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d9711469", "id_comment": "g186338-d9711469-r736860219", "resto": "Sowa_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d9711469-Reviews-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Don\u2019t go with kids", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "4 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "D4203YUgemmas", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d9711469-r736860219-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with my husband and children. I asked for a cake that would be suitable for the children. When I tasted it, it tasted alcoholic. It was! Apparently all the cakes are! We should have been offered our money back really as we did ask specifically. There were no suitable drinks for kids. It\u2019s probably ok to visit without kids."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d9711469", "id_comment": "g186338-d9711469-r734782571", "resto": "Sowa_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d9711469-Reviews-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor service ", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "26 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Cheryl-mac307", "reviewer_origin": ["Carshalton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d9711469-r734782571-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very well presented premise looking really promising but let down by the poor customer service. Took my visiting family for patisseries and hot chocolates. We were made to wait at the counter despite the being the only ones there at the time. I found myself having to repeat my requests and queries and trying to be extra pleasant in the hope of a more welcoming assistance. Service was hostile and off putting to say the least but I didn\u2019t let it deter me from trying to enjoy what seemed to be some really nicely presented patisseries. Unfortunately some of the slices were a bit on the dry side. Not what should be expected when you pay more than \u00a335 on 2 small hot chocolates, 4 slices of cakes and 2 x sodas. Great shame looked so promising. Will not be returning."]}
