{"id_resto": "g186338-d9711469", "id_comment": "g186338-d9711469-r748008391", "resto": "Sowa_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d9711469-Reviews-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good quality patisseries!!", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "27 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "bigbear26", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "188"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "140"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d9711469-r748008391-Sowa_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Having dined at a nearby eatery and not having a dessert, therefore one required a dessert and Sowa Patisserie was right on your doorstep. I purchased a chocolate slice for a family member, along with an apple pie and berry pie (have forgotten the name) \u2013 both being very good. The apple pie had plentiful apple filling which was tart, this was the same with the berry pie. Could not really fault them. I have had produce from this patisserie before and found them to be good."]}
{"id_resto": "g1869831-d1417165", "id_comment": "g1869831-d1417165-r738121574", "resto": "Zaza_Ruislip", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1869831-d1417165-Reviews-Zaza_Ruislip-Ruislip_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Julia!", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "9 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "613lav", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1869831-d1417165-r738121574-Zaza_Ruislip-Ruislip_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We visited here today with friends and ordered starters to share. Our starters were lovely. The main wasn\u2019t to my taste but nothing wrong with it whatsoever just didn\u2019t suit my taste buds. Our lovely waitress Julia made all the difference to our evening. I work in this industry so I know how difficult it is to maintain the level of service she provided during busy time. She was fantastic! Such a great asset to your company! I would employ you in a heartbeat people like you make all the difference in hospitality. This would have been a three star was it not for your great service x"]}
