{"id_resto": "g1096796-d3323113", "id_comment": "g1096796-d3323113-r744525679", "resto": "The_Oxford_Blue", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1096796-d3323113-Reviews-The_Oxford_Blue-Old_Windsor_Windsor_Windsor_and_Maidenhead_Berkshire_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Very disappointing", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "12 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "racse", "reviewer_origin": ["Maidenhead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1096796-d3323113-r744525679-The_Oxford_Blue-Old_Windsor_Windsor_Windsor_and_Maidenhead_Berkshire_England.html", "content": ["4 of us dined at this restaurant. It was our first visit and whilst we thought the meal was average and the staff were friendly enough, I emailed the restaurant directly to raise my concern which was that we were made to feel uncomfortable towards the end of our meal (at about 11pm) getting the distinct impression that it was time for us to leave. The front door was open, the tables were being wiped down and even the hoover came out of the cupboard.", "We didn\u2019t think this was a very nice way to end the evening especially as we\u2019d just spent \u00a3400 with you.", "The restaurant ignored our message."]}
{"id_resto": "g1096796-d3323113", "id_comment": "g1096796-d3323113-r741263925", "resto": "The_Oxford_Blue", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1096796-d3323113-Reviews-The_Oxford_Blue-Old_Windsor_Windsor_Windsor_and_Maidenhead_Berkshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Weekend away", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "26 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Q741TThelent", "reviewer_origin": ["Cardiff, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1096796-d3323113-r741263925-The_Oxford_Blue-Old_Windsor_Windsor_Windsor_and_Maidenhead_Berkshire_England.html", "content": ["I booked this restaurant for somewhere nice to go for a meal on Saturday night. I am so glad I did. The food the service was excellent. We arrived early but that was not a problem. I had the seafood rarebit to start my husband had the pigs trotter. The level of detail was perfect. We had a map to show us where the food was sourced from a lovely touch. Our mains were beef and the pheasant again beautifully presented but most of all perfectly cooked. For dessert my husband had the cheese board but honestly I think I had the best dessert pair parfait. Absolutely gorgeous. Would recommend this place for anyone looking for something a little bit special.", "The service was lovely. Just the right sort of attention I like. Not to over the top but there if needed. ", "Made a lovely weekend away quite special."]}
