{"id_resto": "g191260-d5999531", "id_comment": "g191260-d5999531-r741427494", "resto": "Madhu_s_Heathrow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191260-d5999531-Reviews-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delightful food", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "26 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Stephen B,", "Thank you for taking time and for your comments. We glad to hear that you enjoyed our food here. We look forward to see you soon in Madhus Heathrow again.", "Kind Regards,", "Claudio Fernandes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "312StephenB", "reviewer_origin": ["York, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "107"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191260-d5999531-r741427494-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I visited with 2 work colleagues in January 2020.", "The food was excellent - we had a range of starters to share and then just a main course of chicken. Garlic prawns starter was particularly lovely.", "Few drinks plus service charge and it was just above \u00a350 a head."]}
{"id_resto": "g191260-d5999531", "id_comment": "g191260-d5999531-r735690934", "resto": "Madhu_s_Heathrow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191260-d5999531-Reviews-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Meal", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "30 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Dear Jerry Thefirst,", "Many thanks for taking time and writing your feedback. Our thali as mentioned is one of our most popular guest favourite to order from our menu. We do specialise in our Robata grill which is something we would certainly recommend. Its good to hear that our service was attentive. We look forward to see you back in Madhus Heathrow.", "Kind Regards,", "Claudio Fernandes "], "reviewer_pseudo": "JerryThefirst", "reviewer_origin": ["Folkestone, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191260-d5999531-r735690934-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We weren't expecting an exceptionally good Indian, Punjabi, meal at a Heathrow airport hotel but this really was good. ", "You are offered really good poppadoms and sauces as an appetizer, and they were spicy.", "We had two types of chaat as a starter. Spicy and delicious, on the large size.", "Mains were thali prawns, chicken tikka and takka daal. All delicious, maybe a dish too many as the portions are generous.", "Service was very attentive. Thank you Punam. ", "I thought it was good value for money at \u00a385 including drinks and the service charge. I lived in Birmingham for a long time and have had a fair few curries but this was near the top. ", "Highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g1096796-d3323113", "id_comment": "g1096796-d3323113-r746524417", "resto": "The_Oxford_Blue", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1096796-d3323113-Reviews-The_Oxford_Blue-Old_Windsor_Windsor_Windsor_and_Maidenhead_Berkshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely superb, easily Michelin Star quality... ", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "21 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MartinJones17", "reviewer_origin": ["Brighton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1096796-d3323113-r746524417-The_Oxford_Blue-Old_Windsor_Windsor_Windsor_and_Maidenhead_Berkshire_England.html", "content": ["Can't recommend this place highly enough. We were greeted and served by Liam. He was fabulous and controlled the room brilliantly. I've attached photos of the food so you can see how good the presentation is. The flavours were just sublime and I can honestly say this was the best meal I've had in years, possibly ever. Why this place doesn't have at least 1 Michelin star, I will never know. We will definitely be back. "]}
{"id_resto": "g191260-d5999531", "id_comment": "g191260-d5999531-r739842697", "resto": "Madhu_s_Heathrow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191260-d5999531-Reviews-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent food and service", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "18 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear mathewkurien,", "Thank you for kind comments. We at Madhus always try our best to leave an memorable experience for our guest whoever are dining in. We are glad that our efforts were recognised. We look to forward to welcome you soon in Madhus Heathrow.", "Kind Regards,", "Claudio Fernandes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mathewkurien", "reviewer_origin": ["Buckinghamshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191260-d5999531-r739842697-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We have been to Madhu's Heathrow a few times in the last couple of months and greatly enjoyed the experience. We find the starters here to be wonderful and there was an occasion when we had only starters for our evening meal (several, of course). Our fave starters here are Aloo Tikki, chilli garlic prawns, chicken tikka. I am quite fond of their 'Masaledaar Kuku' and find that it goes quite well with rumali roti. The staff are polite, friendly and attentive - Vinod, Claudio, Sellington to name a few....The place appears to be a big hit with other families too, as most times Madhu's is 'buzzing'"]}
{"id_resto": "g191260-d5999531", "id_comment": "g191260-d5999531-r740954895", "resto": "Madhu_s_Heathrow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191260-d5999531-Reviews-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "This is the best Indian food", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "24 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Andressa D,", "Thank you for taking time and for your comments, Its always good to see our employees name mentioned and on this occasion we are happy to hear that you were well looked after. Hope to see you back very soon.", "Kind Regards,", "Claudio Fernandes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "986andressad", "reviewer_origin": ["Berlin, Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191260-d5999531-r740954895-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["This is the best Indian food I\u2019ve ever had, the lentil soup was a delight! Punam Upreti Neupane, our waitress for the night, was very attentive and efficient by replacing the rice, which came with cumin seeds, without any questions. Both food and service were excellent, and the ambiance was perfect. Thanks for providing such a a great experience <3"]}
{"id_resto": "g191260-d5999531", "id_comment": "g191260-d5999531-r743787095", "resto": "Madhu_s_Heathrow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191260-d5999531-Reviews-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Oh dear", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "8 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Ashutosh S,", "Many thanks for your feedback, We take all our feedback positively and work to improve on it. We are saddened to hear about your experience. I would like to mention here that Madhus always uses quality ingredients and never compromise on it. Our Robata grill here is our house speciality. Your ordered broccoli and gobhi is made right in front of our guest, Papdi chaat as you are aware is an cold appetiser which is mixture of crispy pan cakes, yougurt, tamrind and other spices. Most places have standard way of serving this, so do we. Fried poppadoms are used in our restaurant and its very sad to know you found hair on that which our chefs are now looking into it. ", "Thank you", "Kind Regards,", "Claudio Fernandes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ashtoashes", "reviewer_origin": ["Northampton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191260-d5999531-r743787095-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Broccoli and Cauliflower ", "BBQed with body heat or the cooks breath.Terrible .", "Chaat Papdi ", " I felt as if the papdi had had a bit of naughty rumpy pumpy with moth balls! what\u2019s there in a chaat ?colloquially it means to lick .Signifying that the preparation is so good you lick it ,around here you will only do it if you suffer from hereditary dysgeusia and are on a study cohort that is working to find a cure for it ", "Papadom platter ", "Served with a hair , the hair was either from a head ( wasn\u2019t my bonce for sure, here they are very short and Gray)", "or a face ( wasn\u2019t mine either, your truly is clean shaven ,on the face ! ) why I say with some degree of certainty about its anatomical antecedents because it wasn\u2019t curly, either ways it wasn\u2019t on the menu so I wasn\u2019t expecting it and I didn\u2019t bring it up as I do not work for Alpecin .", "The Chairs", "The chairs have towel rings at the back. Why ?", "5 The Waiting Staff", "Attentive ,welcoming, pleasant .", " Overall", "here I quote the late AA Gill:", "\"This is a restaurant constructed to attract everybody, but will please nobody. It wants to be popular to make money, but without effort or enthusiasm. It is the collective wit of layers of management and consultants, who no doubt all together understand a great deal about catering but plainly very little about hospitality\""]}
{"id_resto": "g191260-d5999531", "id_comment": "g191260-d5999531-r742562894", "resto": "Madhu_s_Heathrow", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g191260-d5999531-Reviews-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing!", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "2 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Lucy-Lee McGill,", "Thank you for writing and for choosing Madhus to celebrate your staff party. Its always good to come across such good feedback. We look forward to see you soon.", "Kind Regards,", "Claudio Fernandes"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LucyBWM", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g191260-d5999531-r742562894-Madhu_s_Heathrow-Hayes_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We went here for our staff party and were greeted by all smiling faces. Very impressed by the food quality and the service. ", "Thanks a lot!"]}
