{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r738931526", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Off the cuff visit", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "13 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Heather W", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r738931526-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["I was looking to take my husband out for a treat. My usual Italian was fully booked so I did a search for other restaurants in my area and Di Paolo came up. We have been to this restaurant before but not for some time, so I called on the day and luckily they had a table as we wanted a fairly early time. Well, I am so glad my other Italian was booked because we had the most amazing meal. I have to say, all three courses were not just good, they were outstanding. We had a bottle of wine, which was on the menu and was one of our favourites, it just got better and better! The staff were both friendly and attentive and very helpful with suggestions and explanations on a couple of dishes. We did have a wonderful evening and can't wait to book in again, and it won't be too long either!!!! Thank you Di Paolo for a great night."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r736096946", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "New Year's Eve Celebration", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "1 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "marylJ5315BL", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r736096946-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["A well organised event to welcome in 2020. Very friendly and attentive service and they remembered that we had previously celebrated the new year at Di Paolo. Our menu choices had to be selected beforehand; each course was beautifully presented and the quality of the dishes extremely high; I particularly enjoyed my fillet of lemon sole main course. They have a good wine list to choose from. The atmosphere was very appropriate for the occasion, the tables decorated with party hats, streamers and poppers;balloons and coloured lighting added to the effect. There was music and an area of the floor set aside for those who wished to dance with an evocative selection of music to pass the rest of the evening to and Auld Lang Syne at midnight. It was great that Maha and all the staff also seemed to be enjoying the occasion. Not the cheapest way of spending the new year but we knew that when we made our reservation and we totally enjoyed ourselves! Oh and they have very clean and presentable washroom facilities."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r737361805", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "servizio con sorriso (a smile)", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "6 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "hermioneluc", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r737361805-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Attended this restaurant for the first time in December - for a lunch to celebrate my wife's birthday.", "The restaurant was not busy - it was mid-week and two weeks before Christmas.", "The service, from the young waitress and then an American lady, who we were to learn was the wife of Paolo (the owner) was quite charming and attentive.", "The food was delicious, starters and mains - portions were such that my wife had to ask to be allowed to take some of her mains dish home (this was of course accommodated).", "This is old 'authentic' style Italian cuisine & service provided in the heart of Gerrards Cross, Buckinghamshire.", "We both thoroughly enjoyed our celebratory lunch and will return again."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r736618039", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A pleasant surprise", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "3 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GrifandMissy", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r736618039-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Attended a wake today at the restaurant and have to say what a very pleasant surprise. The staff were friendly and attentive and the food was just lovely. Many of us who attended are already talking about going back again for a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r740021808", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Group lunch", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "19 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Meldrews2016", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r740021808-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Needed venue for group lunch of 20. Di Poala met the criteria perfectly with our own private area, tables beautifully laid out and organised very well. Food, service and ambience superb. Would", "highly recommended this restaurant for lunch and dinner as well as private functions."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r739270507", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great service and great food", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "15 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "C C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r739270507-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Just before Christmas, we took our daughters and their families to Di Paolo for an early Christmas celebration.", "The welcome from Maha and Emilia got everything off to a good start. The menu was comprehensive and our chosen meals were excellent. This was the best Italian food in this area. Living very close to the Italian border in France, we believe we have the experience to make such a call. This restaurant had excellent food, friendly, attentive service and was also child-friendly. It will be a regular destination for us."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r742651572", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "50th birthday celebration", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "2 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "justinebM7858JS", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r742651572-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["I booked the private dining area for 26 of us at Di Paolo's for my 50th birthday celebration yesterday.", "From my 1st enquiry until the event itself the communication with the owners Maha & Paolo was great.I had booked a magician to entertain us & they were very accommodating with this. ", "The food was superb & the waiting staff were very friendly & efficient. ", "We all had a fantastic evening & would highly recommend the restaurant for any celebration or just an evening meal.", "Thank you for making my special birthday even more special."]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r746331622", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Delicious dinner", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "20 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jlenia A", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r746331622-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["Such great taste of food, I have asked for linguine with seafood (not even on the menu) thanks to the chef I got it, delicious ! ", "The staff is also lovely. ", "Nice atmosphere for my romantic dinner !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d3377354", "id_comment": "g186338-d3377354-r742004054", "resto": "Oriel_Grande_Brasserie", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d3377354-Reviews-Oriel_Grande_Brasserie-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Prefect place for dining before boarding", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "29 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "antonio_leiwk", "reviewer_origin": ["Hong Kong, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d3377354-r742004054-Oriel_Grande_Brasserie-London_England.html", "content": ["Late lunch before flying back home with family. We ordered egg Benedict, seafood risotto and baked salmon fillet All taste very good and enough portion. Dessert is wonderful as well. Service of the staff is friendly yet professional. Value for money as an airport restaurant. Definitely will come back next time.10 out of 10!"]}
{"id_resto": "g499485-d2250293", "id_comment": "g499485-d2250293-r746487908", "resto": "Di_Paolo", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g499485-d2250293-Reviews-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Family Celebratory Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "21 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "richardkD6175BA", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g499485-d2250293-r746487908-Di_Paolo-Gerrards_Cross_Buckinghamshire_England.html", "content": ["The booking for our family lunch for was for 20 people, including 2 children (aged 2 and 4), through to a 91-year old. To add to that challenge, it was also the week of Storm Ciara and Dennis.", "Discussions at the planning stage were friendly and most helpful. On the day, the staff were all discreetly attentive and helpful (one family member was in a wheel chair). My son and I were held up on the M25 due to an accident and so didn't arrive until 2.30 instead of 12.45 - but even that didn't seem to phase the staff. By the time the sweet course was being served we had 'caught up' with the rest of the diners; but this unfortunate difficulty was dealt with so calmly and with no pressure on us to hurry.", "Everyone enjoyed their choice of menu (submitted a few days previously) - all beautifully cooked with a well-judged balance of flavours. The constant happy chatter was a reflection of everyone's pleasure, more succinctly stated by the 4-year old declaring: 'I would like to come here again'.", "Our grateful thanks to Paolo and all his team."]}
