{"id_resto": "g190742-d1553245", "id_comment": "g190742-d1553245-r743000852", "resto": "New_Bettola", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g190742-d1553245-Reviews-New_Bettola-Slough_Berkshire_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Night with Great Food, Great Staff and Great Entertainment!!!!", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "4 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RichardF38", "reviewer_origin": ["Coventry, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "323"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "162"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g190742-d1553245-r743000852-New_Bettola-Slough_Berkshire_England.html", "content": ["We didn't want to eat at our Travel Lodge so went onto TA to see what was about.....this restaurant popped up and boy are we glad we chose to go here!", "The food is stunning (see pictures)....fresh, hot, tasty and good value for money....great choice and a good wine selection also.", "The service was brilliant and everyone was attentive, friendly, professional and attentive. ", "The entertainment is there every 3rd Friday evening (as I recall?)...solo singer...BRILLIANT!!! ", "Rat pack songs through to The 80's......the staff joined in and soon tables were cleared to make a make-shift dance floor. ", "We only planned to stay until 9pm but ended up leaving at 11:30!!!!", "Fab, Fab place....great food, service and entertainment thrown in.....what a find!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g1869831-d4292134", "id_comment": "g1869831-d4292134-r732982106", "resto": "Red_Onion_Cafe", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1869831-d4292134-Reviews-Red_Onion_Cafe-Ruislip_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Christmas Lunch - Gluten Free", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "16 December 2019", "answer_text": ["When we first started our cafe, we wanted families who have different dietary needs to be able to sit together and eat and from your review we seem to have achieved that. Thank you for sharing your experience, it truly makes us smile and makes our day ", "Regards ", "The Red Onion Cafe team "], "reviewer_pseudo": "FunkyGuts", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1869831-d4292134-r732982106-Red_Onion_Cafe-Ruislip_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Went for Christmas lunch with my mum, partner and uncle. I am a veggie and a coeliac, my mum is veggie and the boys are meat eaters.", "I was very impressed with my Christmas dinner, I had gluten free nut roast, stuffing, roast potaoes, brussels, red cabbage, carrots and gravy.", "It is so nice to be able to go somewhere locally and be able to eat 'normally' have the same things as other people with no fuss and especially have gravy!", "My mum had a veggie pie with stuffing and all the trimmings and the boys had a traditional meat Christmas dinner.", "The food was delicious all 4 of us really enjoyed it the staff were really welcoming and friendly would highly recommend."]}
