{"id_resto": "g504182-d4137803", "id_comment": "g504182-d4137803-r733579028", "resto": "The_Grumpy_Mole", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504182-d4137803-Reviews-The_Grumpy_Mole-Sutton_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent service", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "19 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Anita73M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504182-d4137803-r733579028-The_Grumpy_Mole-Sutton_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I am writing today to praise a wonderful service that was received at your restaurant yesterday.", "My family and I were booked in for my mums 70th birthday. My mum had suffered a stroke and since then we have had a rough 2 years. My mum is now in a wheelchair and days out can be a struggle. I cannot praise the team in Cheam enough for their wonderful service and hospitality. In particular Dimo's, he was so lovely and very attentive to us all in particular with my mum. My mum struggles to speak since the stroke but this did not put him off speaking to her directly, this was so refreshing to see. Nothing was too much trouble and we all had an excellent day. ", "We left with happy hearts because of the lovely experience and service . We shall definitely be returning. ", "Keep up the good work!"]}
{"id_resto": "g7940437-d2091217", "id_comment": "g7940437-d2091217-r739531725", "resto": "The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7940437-d2091217-Reviews-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Quantity over quality, if thats your thing", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "16 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ashrafs44", "reviewer_origin": ["Iver Heath, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "134"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "193"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7940437-d2091217-r739531725-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["There are lost of positives about this restaurant. A very big restaurant that can cope with large groups. Portions are massive, starters size of main courses, and main courses bigger enough for two people. Nothing fancy or exotic, standard british fare. Good range of beers etc. The prices are very reasonable. So why not a glowing review? Well the quality of ingredients isn\u2019t great. The meat quality is average .The crumble i had was frozen in the middle and warm on top. The lamb rack was quite bland with a very sweet sauce. Vegetables over cooked , your gran would love this. Colleagues had the steak which they enjoyed. I probably i am a bit snobbish as prefer quality over quantity."]}
