{"id_resto": "g7940437-d2091217", "id_comment": "g7940437-d2091217-r739897003", "resto": "The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7940437-d2091217-Reviews-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Pretty Damn Good !", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "18 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Spachick64", "reviewer_origin": ["Binfield, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "208"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "72"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7940437-d2091217-r739897003-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Went to the restaurant for a departmental team post Christmas lunch . 8 of us . As a company we frequent the bar regularly and the bar food but rarely use the restaurant . The menu is extensive considering this is in essence a gastro pub . Lovely atmosphere , excellent service and as expected , portion sizes are huge ! Represents excellent value for money with starters and desserts around \u00a38 and mains from around \u00a316-25 . Is easily on par with the local airport hotels in terms of standard of food", "Very popular venue for the airport community ", "Pictures of the desserts. The cheese board was to die for !"]}
{"id_resto": "g7940437-d2091217", "id_comment": "g7940437-d2091217-r740929672", "resto": "The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7940437-d2091217-Reviews-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Huge portions, great service", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "24 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "canoninvest", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "98"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7940437-d2091217-r740929672-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We were a party of 4 celebrating a birthday. It has been some years since we have visited The Pheasant and were not dissapointed. Rik seems to have owned this place for ever and ithas improved over those years. We knew the portions were going to be large so we avoided having starters, thank goodness. The portions were indeed very large and the food was delicious.", "We were warmly greeted in the main restaurant by the bar staff and the maitre de. There was no rush to be taken to our table and we could enjoy a drink before our meal, in the comfortable bar area, (PS Rik, your sofas could do with refurbishment, the leatherette covers are badly worn). Our service at the table was excellent, friendly and helpful. Although the meal was a little slow in coming, it did not matter as we were busy talking and in no rush. The food was hot and presented well, it was delicious, but in my case far to much, and I have a good appetite, I had breast and leg of duck and the breast was so big, I had to have the leg in a doggy bag. We didn't have room for desert.", "Well done Rik for keeping your standrds high, and to all of your staff, no wonder this venue is always so busy."]}
