{"id_resto": "g1637599-d2559730", "id_comment": "g1637599-d2559730-r745301174", "resto": "Denny_s_Seafood_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1637599-d2559730-Reviews-Denny_s_Seafood_Restaurant-Chislehurst_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lord Young", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "15 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "gunzph", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1637599-d2559730-r745301174-Denny_s_Seafood_Restaurant-Chislehurst_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Valentine's day weekend was celebrated at Dennys, and the starter and dessert were fantastic.seI had a fantastic starter seafood pancake which was to die for & my other half had the house special that lacked some seasoning.", "My other half had a house special lobster that was very good, & I had the sauted monkfish cooked in creamy coconut sauce.", "The only downside was that the potato's and vegetables were not enough as we thought that we would receive for each of our meals, as a pose to sharing.", "The deserts were very good, & all in all my girlfriend & I utterly enjoyed our evening.", "The lovely touch for the restaurant is that the entrance is a standard railway station, then you open the door & the restaurant is straight ahead.", "There is a lack of space in terms of the tables, but overall we both enjoyed our evening and would recommend as long as you are prepared to pay a little more for you fish."]}
