day - it would have been nice to have a little candle or a small gesture to make it a special occasion, but there was none, especially as we paid more than \u00a3100 for food and drinks.", "The one redeeming feature was that the cocktails were pretty good, so if it is drinks you are after, this place may be a good choice, but you will probably have a long wait before you're served!"]}
