{"id_resto": "g1637599-d2559730", "id_comment": "g1637599-d2559730-r743877067", "resto": "Denny_s_Seafood_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g1637599-d2559730-Reviews-Denny_s_Seafood_Restaurant-Chislehurst_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding restaurant, lovely atmosphere, amazing staff and an all-round fantastic experience", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "9 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "325stefb", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g1637599-d2559730-r743877067-Denny_s_Seafood_Restaurant-Chislehurst_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I live in SE London and really only come to Denny's as a bit of a treat which is wrong, as this place is exceptional. From the appealing, quirky location inside the train station old ticket hall, to the delightful ambience and furnishings, to the superb menu and friendly, efficient staff, this place is first class!!", "I recently took my girlfriend and two friends for a joint birthday meal, and they were overwhelmed to say the least. It was a surprise for two of them, and when we got a taxi to the train station they thought we were getting on a train. As there are no windows looking in from the doorway; Denny's really is a hidden gem. The look on their faces when I opened the door.....", "So all in all, Denny's is outstanding in every way. Even their Irish coffee's and all other variants (Baileys, Calypso etc) are superb, but the staff are all super-knowledgeable about the menu too, and can happily adapt a meal to suit your tastes, with no issues.", "Book a week or so in advance as Denny's is very popular with the locals; many, many regulars go there. Enjoy!!"]}
