{"id_resto": "g504182-d2191893", "id_comment": "g504182-d2191893-r742374741", "resto": "Casa_Nostra", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504182-d2191893-Reviews-Casa_Nostra-Sutton_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Italian food", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "1 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "A784JKdebbier", "reviewer_origin": ["Sutton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504182-d2191893-r742374741-Casa_Nostra-Sutton_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Have visited the Casa Nostra restaurant several times. Food is always consistently excellent and the service very prompt and friendly. The specials are particularly good and changed frequently to whatever is in season. The only downside is the amount of tables that they cram in, making it difficult to have a quiet conversation with the next table literally 2 feet away. Apart from this would definitely recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g504175-d14866695", "id_comment": "g504175-d14866695-r745149492", "resto": "Chakra_Kingston_Riverside", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d14866695-Reviews-Chakra_Kingston_Riverside-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Valentines Dinner", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "15 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Diner Thank you for taking the time to review Chakra Riverside in Kingston upon Thames. Our executive chef Satya and his team take great pride in delivering the menu. Thank you for your comments it means a lot to our team lead by Sunil our GM and we look forward to welcoming you back soon. Kind regards"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Domzabar", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d14866695-r745149492-Chakra_Kingston_Riverside-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Food, service, attentiveness , cocktails and pricing were spot on.", "I\u2019m not one for the usual Indian offerings, but this menu looked great. Not just the standard creamy kormas or masalas etc but well presented smaller dishes with amazing flavours. ", "When we booked we didn\u2019t realise it was a set menu for valentines , and normally we do go for a la carte as most of the time for us on a set menu there is a course which doesn\u2019t sound too appealing.", "This to our surprise was perfect as the 4 courses served each were something new we hadn\u2019t had before and were delicious. The goat curry and sweet potato chaat were incredible. ", "The Martinis ( lychee, espresso, pornstar) we had were made to perfection and food was brought to our table in good time. Kulfi ice cream on a stick was a nice touch and tasted great as it\u2019s normally so fragrant I don\u2019t like it but this one was spot on. ", "Cannot fault this place and the manager and staff were first class. I hope this place sticks around as we will definitely be coming again . Next time probably with the kids as there is also plenty for them to try as well", "Thanks Chakra team"]}
{"id_resto": "g504175-d14866695", "id_comment": "g504175-d14866695-r742844313", "resto": "Chakra_Kingston_Riverside", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d14866695-Reviews-Chakra_Kingston_Riverside-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Soul food", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "3 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Diner Thank you for taking the time to review Chakra Riverside in Kingston upon Thames. Our executive chef Satya and his team take great pride in delivering the menu. Thank you for your comments it means a lot to our team lead by Sunil our GM and we look forward to welcoming you back soon. Kind regards"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CMCPP", "reviewer_origin": ["Kingston upon Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d14866695-r742844313-Chakra_Kingston_Riverside-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We have been visiting Chakra many times since its opening and it never disappoints. The food is just delicious - the flavours very different to the other Indian restaurants we had known before. We like the tables close to the large windows as they allow a nice view on the Thames. Today, our waiter Flo has been - like always - very friendly and attentive. If we come by for a lunch menu or a big dinner - we are always treated as special guests. In our family we are vegans, vegetarians, fish and meat lovers - and all find dishes they love"]}
{"id_resto": "g504175-d14866695", "id_comment": "g504175-d14866695-r746772856", "resto": "Chakra_Kingston_Riverside", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504175-d14866695-Reviews-Chakra_Kingston_Riverside-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Service beyond the call of duty", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "22 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Dear Diner ", "Thank you for taking the time to leave your comments. Yes Dev had mentioned the incident to Management and we are very pleased with the actions he took and look forward to welcoming you to Chakra or having the food delivered to your home. ", "Kind regards "], "reviewer_pseudo": "745keno", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504175-d14866695-r746772856-Chakra_Kingston_Riverside-Kingston_upon_Thames_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Here's a rare experience. I ordered a meal from Chakra via JustEat. It arrived the containers had burst open spilling the contents and making them inedible. Mistakenly, I called the restaurant (should have called JustEat) Dave, the Manager, was very sympathetic, apologised and replaced the food. BUT JustEat wouldn't deliver it! This led to a very unsatisfactory exchange with JustEat. Dave was mortified, even offering to break his bus journey home to drop off our order!!! I won't be using JustEat again - We will be using Chakra many more times."]}
