{"id_resto": "g7940437-d2091217", "id_comment": "g7940437-d2091217-r745083663", "resto": "The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7940437-d2091217-Reviews-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The TOPS", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "14 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Countrywidetraveller", "reviewer_origin": ["Hounslow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7940437-d2091217-r745083663-The_Pheasant_Restaurant_Pheasant_Inn-Harlington_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["The Pheasant Restaurant is by far the bestest place locally to go for ANY celebration. Allways a very warm welcome by The GOVERNOR. From the Bar staff to the Waitng staff, you are always treated with respect and courtesy. Nothing is too much trouble. As for the food....well.....I have never had to mention that something is not right. So much to choose between for all courses. I've had many different starters and the 1 that hits the high notes is the Avocado, Smoked Salmon with Stilton. Wow. Good size portion and SOOOO Much flavour. My only complaint is 1 to myself. I cant do desserts any more, so I miss out on the pleasure of that. No doubt the service and food in the bar are most probably as excellent as it is in this restaurant. As my good friend ARNIE always says.... We'll Be Back"]}
