{"id_resto": "g504182-d4137803", "id_comment": "g504182-d4137803-r736477547", "resto": "The_Grumpy_Mole", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g504182-d4137803-Reviews-The_Grumpy_Mole-Sutton_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Another great meal at a great venue. ", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "3 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "darenk690", "reviewer_origin": ["Morden, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g504182-d4137803-r736477547-The_Grumpy_Mole-Sutton_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We have been here many times and during December went twice. Once for a large family birthday for my mother in law, the staff were lovely enough to bring out her desert with a candle on so that we could sing happy birthday. Most recently was yesterday (2nd January) when it was just four of us including my aunt. We had a great meals. My son had the vegetarian wellington which was very nice, I had the chicken burger and my wife had the lamb which she said was perfectly cooked. The portion sizes were large. My aunts dessert (apple strudel) was actually too big for her). We will certainly be back and look forward to eating there again during 2020. . "]}
