{"id_resto": "g7380842-d12019992", "id_comment": "g7380842-d12019992-r723047672", "resto": "Sougtani_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d12019992-Reviews-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic restaurant!", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "1 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jemmalee3", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "174"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "87"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d12019992-r723047672-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["I came here after reading really good reviews on trip advisor and I\u2019m so glad I did, I love Moroccan food! I ordered lamb Kafta with rice pitta bread & hummus to take away. I will be back to try more on the menu as it does look amazing, the quality of my food was perfect! I was lucky to have the whole restaurant to myself enjoying the nice views outside. My waiter was very friendly & attentive towards me, the service was exceptional and I\u2019m definitely visiting again :-) "]}
{"id_resto": "g7380842-d12019992", "id_comment": "g7380842-d12019992-r723302151", "resto": "Sougtani_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d12019992-Reviews-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Take away", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "2 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mishamarie85", "reviewer_origin": ["Northwood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d12019992-r723302151-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["Ordered from here after a friends recommendation. She dines at the restaurant regularly. I phoned in the order and collected within 30 minutes. The presentation was fantastic, great quality containers are used to serve the food and the portion sizes were generous. My only complaint is that we asked for a particular dish to be made without nuts; this request was not undertaken. I have a severe allergy and this may have been potentially very hazardous if not spotted. The restaurant were apologetic but as they do not offer delivery service They were unable to correct the issue and promised that if I ordered again it would be replaced.. I wasn\u2019t overly satisfied with that response but in all honesty the food was so fantastic that I wouldn\u2019t hesitate to order again. Food was", "Fresh, well seasoned and packaged with great care. I will book a table to dine in shortly."]}
{"id_resto": "g7380842-d12019992", "id_comment": "g7380842-d12019992-r726880449", "resto": "Sougtani_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d12019992-Reviews-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A lovely vibe", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "16 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Cat W", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d12019992-r726880449-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["The light is too bright; the noise is too loud; the waiters are rushed off their feet; you order by the number on the menu; you pay at the counter; there is no publicity about BYO. ", "But the food is fabulous. Stick around, be patient, the waiters are good guys, just drink something, relax and enjoy a night in a great restaurant in Pinner."]}
{"id_resto": "g7380842-d12019992", "id_comment": "g7380842-d12019992-r736852386", "resto": "Sougtani_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d12019992-Reviews-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing variety, great ambience, delicious food and friendly owner!", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "4 January 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MSQuirks", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d12019992-r736852386-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["As far as restaurants go, this place is absolutely perfect. In the last year we must have visited this place atleast 5-6 times and the level of service, quality and variety of vegetarian food, and the smile on the owners face has never dropped one bit. We recently went to another Lebanese restaurant in our area in the hope of trying a new place, but were so disappointed partly because the place was average but also because the bar has been set so high by sougtani. The owner is a young humble man who ensures his customers are happy and in one of our visits even packed a portion of beetroot hummus for my little one as he loved it so much. I highly recommend this place to everyone. If you want to try authentic Lebanese food with great friendly staff in a well presented restaurant, this place is for you. Offcourse the BYOB, complimentary mint tea and baklava are also a fine touch. "]}
{"id_resto": "g7380842-d12019992", "id_comment": "g7380842-d12019992-r733982444", "resto": "Sougtani_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g7380842-d12019992-Reviews-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent service and food", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "21 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "kenzach1", "reviewer_origin": ["Bergen, Norway"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g7380842-d12019992-r733982444-Sougtani_Restaurant-Pinner_Greater_London_England.html", "content": ["We tried the recommended mix of starters and mains. Delicious. And very friendly and attentive staff. Walking distance from the tube-station in a cosy NW-London village."]}
