{"id_resto": "g186338-d734325", "id_comment": "g186338-d734325-r732228495", "resto": "Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d734325-Reviews-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "12 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Billythevid", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d734325-r732228495-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "content": ["We were late and had to delay our start time twice, and it was a Sunday!! Did it phase them? Not a bit. We'd already had a really good meal a month previously and this was a return visit with relations form the USA. They were an hour late. The restaurant did everything to make our meal as unstressed and as appetising as possible. And they achieved it. Another memorable meal. Try them. And don't be late!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d734325", "id_comment": "g186338-d734325-r742611638", "resto": "Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d734325-Reviews-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A welcome addition to fine dining in Chiswick, West London", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "2 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Woibam", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d734325-r742611638-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I went on a Saturday night and enjoyed ourselves tremendously. The food was excellent and the wine list sufficiently comprehensive without being overwhelming. Initially, when we arrived, the service could have been a little quicker and more attentive. I hate it if I have to wait to be shown my table and then nothing happens for quite a while. However, when things got underway, you can't complain. Service was good and efficient. all in all, a place we want to go back to. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d734325", "id_comment": "g186338-d734325-r732593177", "resto": "Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d734325-Reviews-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Gem in Chiswick! ", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "14 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "dariia m", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d734325-r732593177-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my family had visited this outstanding restaurant last night! First of all, the location of the place is very easy to get to and practically on the Main Street, however it is in a quite street which is great for anyone parking. When we walked in, we were delighted to see a small but very cozy and comforting place with touches of green shades! We were treated with a smile, and had been sat at the best table, in my opinion. It was a lovely side table with huge window to outside and quite spot! Our waiter was the most friendly, and admirable person I\u2019ve ever met! He was doing he\u2019s job at the best and enjoyed it as well! The food was cooked to the perfect extend! The portion sizes are not big but very tasty and amazing representation! But Francesco had made our day! He was very delightful and easy to talk to, he makes the place a gem in Chiswick! Will be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d734325", "id_comment": "g186338-d734325-r735795056", "resto": "Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d734325-Reviews-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Divine", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "31 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MG92812", "reviewer_origin": ["Blunham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d734325-r735795056-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "content": ["We took clients to Restaurant Michael Nadra for a pre-Christmas lunch and I could not recommend it enough. BEAUTIFUL food, lovely atmosphere, really just perfect service. We are sad that we don't live closer as we would be regulars!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d734325", "id_comment": "g186338-d734325-r745162333", "resto": "Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d734325-Reviews-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A hidden gem in the heart of Chiswick", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "15 February 2020", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Superhaq", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "98"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d734325-r745162333-Restaurant_Michael_Nadra_Chiswick-London_England.html", "content": ["I love coming here. The food is always impeccable. The presentation is fantastic. The flavours are perfect. It\u2019s an absolute hidden gem. I love coming here for lunch. The menu changes regularly so there\u2019s no room for getting bored with mundane know-by-heart menus. A great reason to keeping going back and a wonderful place for a date or quiet evening meal too."]}
